{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "沈浪与熊猫儿在酒楼遇一神秘小老人，老人自称残疾不能起身相迎，实则双腿藏有淬毒利剑。老人邀沈浪品酒，两人以七杯调酒为名暗中较量内力，沈浪识破老人在第七杯酒中下毒，当场揭穿其身份——关外快活酒使韩伶。韩伶恼羞成怒，以腿中剑偷袭沈浪，沈浪从容避开，韩伶破窗逃走。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此便请过来如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "遵命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请恕老朽失礼，不能站起相迎……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因老朽有个最好的理由请公子原谅此点……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么理由？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呃……这……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "足下已满意了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请恕在下……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他再也不去瞧熊猫儿一眼，目光回向沈浪时，面上又露出笑容，微微笑道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢座。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上难求知己，何妨杯中寻觅。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙，妙极。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "足下既知酒，且请尽此一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好酒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是什么酒，足下可尝得出？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但若非老丈妙手调成，酒味又岂能如此奇妙？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，且让在下再尝一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此！老朽调制此酒，倒也花了不少心思，是以便为此酒取了个名字，唤作唐老太太的撒手锏……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台终于回来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对，还是一大杯一大杯的烧刀子喝着干脆。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想乔兄倒是小弟知己，来，敬你一杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我想喝？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是喝不着，所以就说不好了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，喝不到的酒，永远是酸的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你却也莫要当他这几杯酒是容易喝的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此话怎讲？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他喝这几杯酒，当真不知费了多少气力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为别人替他倒酒，他才费气力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "越说越不懂了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非但你不懂，我也糊涂得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们再仔细瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在沈相公举起了酒杯，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在……那老儿举起了酒樽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯……接着往下瞧，瞧仔细些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在，那老儿将酒樽歪了下去……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在，那老儿瓶口已碰着沈浪酒杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，现在他开始倒酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还瞧不出奇怪么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这又有什么奇……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是了。但他倒酒为何特别慢？这原因你已瞧出？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非他正拼命用力气？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你倒再瞧沈相公。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他那酒杯难道缺了个口么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这酒樽的瓶口已弯了……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "依我看，还是沈相公占了上风。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒是实话。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "乔五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯，这话也不错……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好酒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此说来，这第七杯酒想必更妙了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙与不妙，一尝便知。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这老儿倒也奇怪，明知内力不及沈浪，为何还要……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "相公莫非要自己倒酒？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "相公这是为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老丈这第七杯酒，在下万万不敢拜领。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因那六杯酒喝得，这第七杯酒却是喝不得的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此话……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自是要奉还的，但……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁，你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，在下今生只怕也喝不着第八杯酒了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认得我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来自关外，酒中之使……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_si_gu",
      "speaker_name": "花四姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想他行藏虽如此隐秘，却还是被沈相公瞧破了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下猜的可不错么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "厉害厉害……不错不错……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，不知大名可否见告？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老朽韩伶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_ling",
      "speaker_name": "韩伶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只惭愧老朽全无刘伶荷锄饮酒的豪兴。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
